===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{term|abedde|lang=enm}}, {{m|ang|on}} {{term|bedde||bed|lang=ang}}, from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{term|bedd||bed|lang=ang}}. Equivalent to {{prefix|a|bed|t1=in, on|lang=en}}.

===Pronunciation===
* {{a|RP}} {{IPA|/əˈbɛd/|lang=en}}
* {{a|US}} {{IPA|/əˈbɛd/|lang=en}}
* {{rhymes|ɛd|lang=en}}

